UPDATE public.questions SET
  stimulus_text = 'The process of making a film is long and complex, involving many people with specialized skills. The director is often the key figure, guiding the actors, crew, and other creative personnel toward a shared vision. Even the director, however, must be able to rely on the contributions of others, such as the cinematographer, who determines the look of the film, and the editor, who shapes the narrative structure. Each of these specialists brings a different perspective and set of skills to the project, contributing to the final product.',
  question_text = 'Which choice provides the best punctuation for the underlined portion of the sentence? ',
